=== 影響 ===
拿破崙曾建立了[[華沙公國|華沙公國]]，但他失敗后的維也納會議使局勢對波蘭人更加不利。俄國獲得了更多波蘭領土。在鎮壓了[[十一月起义|1831年的起義]]後，[[華沙公國|華沙公國]]的自治權被取消，波蘭人的財産被沒收充公，強徴入伍，大學也被關閉。1863年的起義之後，波蘭被強制推行俄化的中學教育，文化程度出現大幅下降。在奧地利部分，波蘭人成了二等公民，允許在國會派出代表和建立自己的大學，[[盧布林|盧布林]]和[[克拉科夫|克拉科夫]]成為波蘭教育的中心。與此同時，普魯士將波蘭的整套教育系統德國化，較俄國而言完全不尊重波蘭人的文化和制度。

拜[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]以及[[1917年俄国革命|俄國革命]]的混亂狀態所賜，根據戰後的《[[凡爾賽和約|凡爾賽和約]]》，波蘭終于在亡國的123年後恢復了獨立。

瓜分迫使波蘭人尋找機會改變現狀。<ref name="LRJohnson">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=e_m13Hk3AFEC&pg=PA128&ots=R9iFhEIGFV&dq=%22partitions+of+Poland%22&as_brr=3&sig=Kw4fmCPIq_ATgIZQSAr0N6S5IlA&hl=en|publisher=Oxford University Press|date=1996-10-31|isbn=978-0-19-802607-5|language=en|first=Lonnie|last=Johnson|title=Central Europe: Enemies, Neighbors, Friends|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412000306/https://books.google.com/books?id=e_m13Hk3AFEC&pg=PA128&ots=R9iFhEIGFV&dq=%22partitions+of+Poland%22&as_brr=3&sig=Kw4fmCPIq_ATgIZQSAr0N6S5IlA&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>許多波蘭的詩人、政治家、貴族、作家、藝術家被流放（造就了名詞“[[大移民潮|大遷徙]]”），成為19世紀的革命者。對獨立和自由的渴望也成了[[波蘭浪漫主義|波蘭浪漫主義]]定義的一部分。<ref name="WHZaw">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hwZASJRHjLIC&pg=PA330&dq=Polish+romantic+revolutionaries&sig=kGTiU4OwRfAtsNi0kbNSbfODuBg&hl=en|publisher=Clarendon Press|date=1993|isbn=978-0-19-820303-2|language=en|first=W. H.|last=Zawadzki|title=A Man of Honour: Adam Czartoryski as a Statesman of Russia and Poland, 1795-1831|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412000309/https://books.google.com/books?id=hwZASJRHjLIC&pg=PA330&dq=Polish+romantic+revolutionaries&sig=kGTiU4OwRfAtsNi0kbNSbfODuBg&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="StefanAuer">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=b2IRot3UaQ0C&pg=RA2-PA60&ots=Xyinrgi2Jf&dq=Polish+romantic+revolutionaries&sig=aL7G6NL27FzH1&hl=en|publisher=Taylor & Francis|date=2004-01-22|isbn=978-0-203-56129-4|language=en|first=Stefan|last=Auer|title=Liberal Nationalism in Central Europe|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412000316/https://books.google.com/books?id=b2IRot3UaQ0C&pg=RA2-PA60&ots=Xyinrgi2Jf&dq=Polish+romantic+revolutionaries&sig=aL7G6NL27FzH1&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>波蘭革命者參與了在[[普魯士|普魯士]]、[[奧地利帝國|奧地利帝國]]、[[俄罗斯沙皇国|沙皇俄國]]的起義。<ref name="DieterDowe">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=B3qRFCn5CHoC&pg=PA180&dq=Polish+romantic+revolutionaries&sig=cOYtkxH_i8lEX_0VUMEVhwGLVWs&hl=en|publisher=Berghahn Books|date=2001|isbn=978-1-57181-164-6|language=en|first=Dieter|last=Dowe|first2=Heinz-Gerhard|last2=Haupt|first3=Dieter|last3=Langewiesche|first4=Jonathan|last4=Sperber|title=Europe in 1848: Revolution and Reform|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412000322/https://books.google.com/books?id=B3qRFCn5CHoC&pg=PA180&dq=Polish+romantic+revolutionaries&sig=cOYtkxH_i8lEX_0VUMEVhwGLVWs&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[波蘭軍團|波蘭軍團]]曾與[[拿破崙|拿破崙]]並肩作戰。<ref name="Carrib">{{Cite web|title=Poland's Caribbean Tragedy|url=http://www.hartford-hwp.com/archives/43a/038.html|accessdate=2020-07-11|work=www.hartford-hwp.com|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312202316/http://www.hartford-hwp.com/archives/43a/038.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NapSoc">{{Cite web|title=INS Scholarship 1998: Polish Projects of Napoleon Bonaparte|url=https://www.napoleon-series.org/ins/scholarship98/c_polish.html|accessdate=2020-07-11|work=www.napoleon-series.org|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413125018/https://www.napoleon-series.org/ins/scholarship98/c_polish.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在“為了我們和妳們的自由”的口號下，波蘭人廣泛參與了[[1848年革命|1848年革命]]（尤其是匈牙利革命）。<ref name="DieterDowe"/><ref name="Fofay2">{{Cite web|title=Gods, Heroes, & Legends|url=http://www.globalprovince.com/ghl.htm|accessdate=2020-07-11|work=www.globalprovince.com|archive-date=2021-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702025837/http://www.globalprovince.com/ghl.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>


